# Flat Fee Delivery

Add a short description here. You can also add a screenshot if needed.

## Installation

### Manually

* Copy the module into ```<thelia_root>/local/modules/``` directory and be sure that the name of the module is FlatFeeDelivery.
* Activate it in your thelia administration panel

### Composer

Add it in your main thelia composer.json file

```
composer require your-vendor/flat-fee-delivery-module:~1.0
```

## Usage

First you need to activate the module in the back-office. Then you can add shipping zones with the button "Shipping zones".
With this module you can use a flat fee delivery for the areas attached to the module. For that you just have to enter the price you want for each area in the module configuration in the back-office.

## Hook

This module uses the module configuration hook with the module id as a parameter that is used in the loop.


## Loop

This module uses the area loop to list all the areas attached to the module.
